{"name":"Pilot/Ship Captain","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"journal-links":{"references":{}},"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.7w65EIgR0PjvvXF0"},"cf":{"id":"temp_vjikafm48ed","path":"Savage Eberron Rules#/CF_SEP/1. Character Creation#/CF_SEP/1.2. Character Concepts","color":"#000000"}},"content":"<p>Commanders and pilots of elemental bound vehicles, such as lightning rails, wind galleons, or the new air ships. Pilots are often members of House Lyrandar or House Orien. However there are those who are just teamsters in caravans, or ship masters from the Lhazaar Principalities.</p>\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Athletics, Boating, Common Knowledge, Cosmology, Gambling, Piloting, Repair</p>\n<p><strong>Background Edges:</strong> Natural Swimmer</p>\n<p><strong>Leadership Edges:</strong> Any leadership edge</p>\n<p><strong>Professional Edges:</strong> Ace, Acrobat, Boarder, Rope Monkey</p>\n<p><strong>Weird Edges:</strong> Storm Chaser, Wind Sense</p>","_id":"GxEQZTj2qITwhpWd"}
