{"name":"Powers Summary List","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_3t20aa8en26","path":"Savage Eberron Rules#/CF_SEP/4. Magic#/CF_SEP/4.1. Using Magic","color":"#000000"},"journal-links":{"references":{"Item":["N1SLToiXlQTaDlpy"]}}},"content":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<div class=\"header\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<p>Powers Sumamry List</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Forbidden Powers:</strong> <em>Drain Power Points</em></p>\n<p><strong>Renamed Powers: </strong><em>Detect/Conceal Arcana, Teleport</em></p>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<h2>Articles on the Use of Magic</h2>\n<div class=\"swade-columns\">\n<h3>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Using Magic]{Using Magic}</h3>\n<h3>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Arcane Backgrounds]{Arcane Backgrounds}</h3>\n<h3>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Power Modifiers]{Powers Modifiers}</h3>\n<h3>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Powers Summary List]{Powers Summary list}</h3>\n<h3>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Rituals]{Rituals}</h3>\n</div>\n<table class=\"table summary-table\"><caption class=\"table-caption\">\n<h2 class=\"table-title\">Powers</h2>\n</caption>\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"table-header-row\">\n<th class=\"table-column-header\">Power</th>\n<th class=\"table-column-header\">Rank</th>\n<th class=\"table-column-header\">Modifier</th>\n<th class=\"table-column-header\">Range</th>\n<th class=\"table-column-header\" style=\"width: 9%;\">Dur</th>\n<th class=\"table-column-header\">Summary</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Accelerate Healing]{Accelerate Healing}</td>\n<td>V</td>\n<td>&minus;2</td>\n<td>T</td>\n<td>24H</td>\n<td>Target makes @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Healing]{natural healing} every six hours, with +2 on a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{raise}.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Analyze Foe]{Analyze Foe}</td>\n<td>N</td>\n<td>&minus;1</td>\n<td>Sm x2</td>\n<td>1m/R</td>\n<td>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{Opposed Roll} vs @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Spirit} for +1 to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Trait} rolls effecting target and &minus;1 to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Trait} rolls effecting caster. +2 and &minus;2 on a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{raise}.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Animate War Tree]{Animate War Tree}</td>\n<td>H</td>\n<td>&minus;10</td>\n<td>T</td>\n<td>1H/R</td>\n<td>Awakens a tree as a war tree. It is a wild card on a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{raise}.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Arcane Protection]{Arcane Protection}</td>\n<td>N</td>\n<td>&minus;1</td>\n<td>Sm</td>\n<td>1m/R</td>\n<td>Enemy casters subtract 2 (4 with a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{raise}) when targeting this character; reduces @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Damage]{damage} a like amount.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Augury]{Augury}</td>\n<td>N</td>\n<td>&minus;3</td>\n<td>Self</td>\n<td>I</td>\n<td>Recieve an omen about a specific course of action.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Banish]{Banish}</td>\n<td>V</td>\n<td>&minus;3</td>\n<td>Sm</td>\n<td>I</td>\n<td>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{Opposed Roll} vs @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Spirit} to <em>banish</em>&nbsp;entities.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Barrier]{Barrier}</td>\n<td>S</td>\n<td>&minus;2</td>\n<td>Sm</td>\n<td>1m/R</td>\n<td>Creates 5\" (10 yards) long, 1\" (2 yards) tall, @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Breaking Things]{Hardness} 10 barrier.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Battle Song]{Battle Song}</td>\n<td>S</td>\n<td>&minus;1</td>\n<td>MBT</td>\n<td>1m/R</td>\n<td>Grants @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Berserk]{Berserk} to creatures within @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Area Effect Attacks]{Medium Blast Template}.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Beast Friend]{Beast Friend}</td>\n<td>N</td>\n<td>Special</td>\n<td>Sm</td>\n<td>10m/R</td>\n<td>Controls animals.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Becalm]{Becalm}</td>\n<td>S</td>\n<td>Special</td>\n<td>Sm xMiles</td>\n<td>1H/R</td>\n<td>Halves @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Vehicle Notes]{Top Speed}&nbsp;of a ship. +2 to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Boating] rolls in a storm.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Bind Entity]{Bind Entity}</td>\n<td>V</td>\n<td>Special</td>\n<td>Sm</td>\n<td>24H</td>\n<td>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{Opposed Roll} vs @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Spirit} to bind a summoned entity.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Blast]{Blast}</td>\n<td>S</td>\n<td>&minus;2</td>\n<td>Sm x2</td>\n<td>I</td>\n<td>2d6 @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Damage]{Damage} in a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Area Effect Attacks]{Medium Blast Template}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Blind]{Blind}</td>\n<td>N</td>\n<td><span class=\"fontstyle0\">&minus;2</span></td>\n<td>Sm</td>\n<td>I</td>\n<td>Inflicts -2/-4 penalty to victims.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Bolt]{Bolt}</td>\n<td>N</td>\n<td>&minus;1</td>\n<td>Sm x2</td>\n<td>1m/R</td>\n<td>2d6 ranged attac