ound}</td>\n<td>S</td>\n<td>&minus;4</td>\n<td>LBT</td>\n<td>1m/R</td>\n<td>In @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Blast Templates]{Large Blast Template} supernatural creatures need to make @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Spirit} or &minus;2 (&minus;4 on @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{raise}) to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Trait} rolls.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Create Food and Drink]{Create Food and Drink}</td>\n<td>S</td>\n<td>&minus;3</td>\n<td>Sm</td>\n<td>24H</td>\n<td>Create food and water for three humanoids.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Creation]{Creation}</td>\n<td>S</td>\n<td>&minus;3</td>\n<td>Sm</td>\n<td>1H/R</td>\n<td>Create 1 cubic foot per rank og nonliving matter.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Curse]{Curse}</td>\n<td>S</td>\n<td>&minus;3</td>\n<td>T</td>\n<td>Perm</td>\n<td>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{Opposed Roll} vs @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Spirit} or target suffers a level of @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fatigue] each day at sunset.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Damage Field]{Damage Field}</td>\n<td>S</td>\n<td>&ndash;3</td>\n<td>Sm</td>\n<td>1m/R</td>\n<td>Creates aura that causes 2d4 damage.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Darksight]{Darksight}</td>\n<td>N</td>\n<td>&ndash;1</td>\n<td>Sm</td>\n<td>1H/R</td>\n<td>Ignore up to 4 points of @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Illumination]{Illumination} penalties, or 6 with a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{raise}.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Deflection]{Deflection}</td>\n<td>N</td>\n<td>&ndash;2</td>\n<td>Sm</td>\n<td>1m/R</td>\n<td>&minus;2/&ndash;4 to atta